about.description:
Google Cloud’s Phishing Protection countermeasure platform helps to detect phishing attacks against your users. Phishing Protection API enables you to submit URLs suspected to be unsafe. Any URLs that are confirmed to match the Safe Browsing Policies will be added to the Safe Browsing list, which is used by over three billion devices to show warnings when a user visits a known unsafe web resource. Common sources of these URLs are customer reports or internal phishing detection results.
See the [quick start guide](https://googleapis.dev/python/phishingprotection/latest/index.html#quick-start).

name: google-cloud-phishing-protection
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "google-cloud-phishing-protection" %}
{% set version = "0.3.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "e4525ac0274bb4d70811e7148483ebae74d892567975d8a0f9a5053fc7e4480d" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip >=18.1
  run:
    - python
    - google-api-core-grpc >=1.14.0,<2.0.0dev
    - enum34

test:
  imports:
    - grpc
    - google.cloud.phishingprotection
    - google.cloud.phishingprotection_v1beta1

about:
  home: https://github.com/googleapis/python-phishingprotection
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Phishing Protection API client library'
  description: Google Cloud’s Phishing Protection countermeasure platform helps to detect phishing attacks
    against your users. Phishing Protection API enables you to submit URLs suspected to be unsafe. Any URLs
    that are confirmed to match the Safe Browsing Policies will be added to the Safe Browsing list, which is
    used by over three billion devices to show warnings when a user visits a known unsafe web resource. Common
    sources of these URLs are customer reports or internal phishing detection results.

    See the [quick start guide](https://googleapis.dev/python/phishingprotection/latest/index.html#quick-start).

  doc_url: https://googleapis.dev/python/phishingprotection/latest/index.html
  dev_url: https://github.com/googleapis/python-phishingprotection

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - parthea
